Iterates through the three color channels and changes the output color on the
on-shield TriColor ChipLED using the :zephyr:ref:`PWM driver API <pwm_api>`.
That are:

| :hwftlbl-led:`R` : :dts:`aliases { red-pwm-led = &pwm_led_r; };`
| :hwftlbl-led:`G` : :dts:`aliases { green-pwm-led = &pwm_led_g; };`
| :hwftlbl-led:`B` : :dts:`aliases { blue-pwm-led = &pwm_led_b; };`

